<descript>
<abstract>Federation of Saint Kitts and Nevis, 1984 is a scanned map the Caribbean country Federation of Saint Kitts and Nevis at a scale of 20,000. The map is comprised with two sheets and georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
</descript>
